OL,5, Police have released images of the     
OL,6, "very limited view" from a frozen      
OL,7, windscreen in a dangerous driving case 
OL,8, as a warning to other motorists.       
OL,10,FDavid Hyslop, 54, was stopped by       
OL,11,Fofficers on the A701 in Dumfries in    
OL,12,FDecember last year.                    
OL,14,FHe was later found guilty of dangerous 
OL,15,Fdriving, fined #500 and given a        
OL,16,F12-month driving ban.                  
OL,18,FInsp Gavin McHallum urged other drivers
OL,19,Fto make sure their windscreens were    
OL,20,Fclear before setting off.              
